## Performance

### Benchmark Results

Tested against toon-llm v1.0.0b6 (November 2025):

| Test | toon-parser | toon-llm | Speedup |
|------|--------|----------|---------|
| Small Object Decode | 16.1 Î¼s | 94.7 Î¼s | **5.9x** |
| Tabular Small Decode | 46.0 Î¼s | 144.2 Î¼s | **3.1x** |
| Tabular Large Decode (1k rows) | 220.2 Î¼s | 905.9 Î¼s | **4.1x** |
| Mixed Array Decode | 21.1 Î¼s | 102.8 Î¼s | **4.9x** |
| Small Object Encode | 36.3 Î¼s | 278.1 Î¼s | **7.7x** |
| Tabular Large Encode (1k rows) | 325.4 Î¼s | 969.9 Î¼s | **3.0x** |

**Average: 5.82x faster** (range: 2.98x - 9.68x)

See [PERFORMANCE.md](PERFORMANCE.md) for detailed analysis.

